results.cleanName: Legend of Blue Eyes White Dragon Booster Pack 25th Anniversary Edition

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value:
For years, you could only get your hands on these coveted packs as part of the Legendary Collection, but now, just in time to celebrate the 25th anniversary of the card game, theyâ€™re being made available as standalone booster packs!

Legend of Blue Eyes White Dragon was notable not just for being the first booster set, but also for introducing famous cards like Exodia the Forbidden One, as well as incredible Spell Cards like Pot of Greed and Raigeki. This printing will feature both Secret Rares from the set.

Each Legend of Blue Eyes White Dragon Booster Pack (25th Anniversary Edition) contains 9 cards.
